::Striker::

Striker looks down at his freezing scanner. According to it, the two bots he 
had detected (Rowdy Wolf and Zyber) were not far away. He moves on, coming 
closer and closer to the position of the two bots.

Internal Comp: "Warning. Further loss of mech fluid may cause system falure."

Striker sighs and looks down at his fried and beaten chest plate. There was 
mech fluid dripping from it, and a trail of mech fluid was behind him. He 
walks on, hoping to get to the bots before he goes into stasis lock.
